    <h2>About Olaf Martens</h2>
 

  <p>Olaf Martens was born in 1963 in Halle. He studied photography at the Leipzig Hochschule fur Graphik und Buchkunst. Since 1990 he has been freelancing as a photographer in the field of fashion/beauty, journalism and people for magazines like Stern, Der Spiegel, Geo, Frankfurter Allgemeine amongst others. Over the years he has been exhibiting in Bonn, Dresden, Berlin, Munich, Moskou, Rotterdam, Berlin and Lyon. Olaf Martens lives in Leipzig<br />
</p>

